在美國，《光芒萬丈》發行首週空降[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《告示牌》二百強專輯榜]]亞軍位置<ref name="bb1998">{{cite journal|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HwoEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA100#v=onepage&q&f=false|title=Between the Bullets|date=1998-11-14|accessdate=2010-07-11|work=Billboard|issn=0006-2510|volume=110|issue=46|page=100|journal=|archive-date=2017-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170306005549/https://books.google.com/books?id=HwoEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA100#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯以371,000張的銷量打破{{tsl|en|Nielsen SoundScan|尼爾森銷量統計系統|尼爾森銷量統計系統}}有紀錄以來的女性歌手最高首週銷量紀錄<ref name="bb1998"/>。然而專輯當週銷量不敵電影《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|鐵達尼號]]》的{{tsl|en|Titanic (soundtrack)|鐵達尼號-電影原聲帶|原聲帶}}，成為瑪丹娜第五張亞軍專輯<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1045695/first-day-sales-put-madonna-on-track-for-7th-no-1 | title=First day sales put Madonna on track for 7th No. 1 | work=Billboard | first=Keith | last=Caulfield | date=2008-04-30 | accessdate=2008-05-07 | archive-date=2013-05-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529025444/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1045695/first-day-sales-put-madonna-on-track-for-7th-no-1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。專輯以次週以225,000張的銷量繼續被原聲帶壓在亞軍位置<ref name="ruletheworld">{{cite news|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/madonna-once-again-rules-the-world-19980321|title=Madonna Once Again Rules The World|work=Rolling Stone|date=1998-03-21|accessdate=2011-08-19|archive-date=2012-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627173658/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/madonna-once-again-rules-the-world-19980321|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2000年3月16日，專輯獲[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]認證為[[RIAA认证|四白金唱片]]，代表專輯於當地的出貨量達到四百萬張<ref name="riaa"/>。瑪丹娜憑此成為首位擁有七張獲美國唱片業協會認證為多白金唱片的女歌手<ref name="platinumrecord">{{cite journal|title=Titanic Hits 10 Million Mark In April RIAA certifications|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=QQ0EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA10&dq=Madonna+Gold+and+Platinum+Billboard&hl=es&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwi26Z7J-urSAhVC1WMKHVV3BLUQ6AEIQjAH#v=onepage&q=Madonna%20Gold%20and%20Platinum%20Billboard&f=false|first=Carrie|last=Bell|date=1998-05-16|accessdate=2017-03-22|work=Billboard|issn=0006-2510|volume=110|issue=20|page=10|journal=|archive-date=2019-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191216062644/https://books.google.com/books?id=QQ0EAAAAMBAJ#v=onepage&q=Madonna%20Gold%20and%20Platinum%20Billboard&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>根據尼爾森銷量統計系統，《光芒萬丈》截至2016年12月已在美國賣出超過389萬張<ref name="ussales">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7617649/ask-billboard-madonnas-career-album-sales|title=Ask Billboard: Madonna's Career Album Sales|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2016-12-11|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2016-12-12|archive-date=2016-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161212105609/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7617649/ask-billboard-madonnas-career-album-sales|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外專輯亦從[[貝塔斯曼音樂集團|貝塔斯曼]]等唱片俱樂部渠道售出超過459,000張<ref name="BMG">{{cite web |author=Barry David |title=Shania, Backstreet, Britney, Eminem and Janet Top All-Time Sellers |publisher=Music Industry News Network |date=2003-02-18 |url=http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=47877 |accessdate=2011-09-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090817152522/http://www.mi2n.com/press.php3?press_nb=47877 |archivedate=2009-08-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在加拿大，專輯發行首週以59,900張的銷量空降[[加拿大专辑榜|加拿大专辑榜]]冠軍位置<ref name="canadadebut">{{cite news|url=http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/M/Madonna/2005/11/23/1319566-ca.html|title=Madonna dances to No. 1 in Canada|work={{tsl|en|Jam!}}|date=2005-11-23|last=Williams|first=John|accessdate=2009-08-05|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121209143528/http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/M/Madonna/2005/11/23/1319566-ca.html|archivedate=2012-12-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。專輯其後獲[[加拿大音乐协会|加拿大音乐协会]]認證為七白金唱片，代表於當地出貨量達到700,000張<ref name="cria"/>。專輯亦於大洋洲獲得商業成功，包括空降澳洲與紐西蘭專輯榜榜首，並分別獲[[澳大利亚唱片业协会|澳大利亚唱片业协会]]與[[新西兰唱片音乐协会|新西兰唱片音乐协会]]認證為三白金唱片與金唱片，各代表達到210,000張與7,500張的出貨量<ref name="aria"/><ref name="rianz"/>。

在英國，《光芒萬丈》首週空降[[英國專輯排行榜|英國專輯排行榜]]冠軍位置，並連續兩週高據榜首<ref name="uk"/>。專輯其後獲[[英国唱片业协会|英国唱片业协会]]認證為六白金唱片，代表於當地出貨量達到180萬張<ref name="bpi"/>。在法國，專輯首週空降專輯榜亞軍位置，並連續七週逗留在同一位置<ref name="hungmedien"/>。專輯其後[[法國唱片出版業公會|法國唱片出版業公會]]認證為三白金唱片，代表專輯的出貨量達到900,000張<ref name="infodisc"/>。而專輯於當地的實際銷量則達到925,400張<ref name="infodisc">{{cite web |url=http://www.infodisc.fr/CDCertif_P3.php?debut=50 |title=Les Albums Triple Platine |publisher=[[法國唱片出版業公會|Syndicat National de l'Édition Phonographique]] |accessdate=2010-11-30 |language= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111223203021/http://www.infodisc.fr/CDCertif_P3.php?debut=50 |archivedate=2011-12-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在德國，專輯最高登上[[GfK娱乐榜单|GfK娱乐榜单]]第1位，並蟬聯榜首長達七星期<ref name="germany"/>。專輯獲[[聯邦音樂產業協會|聯邦音樂產業協會]]認證為三白金唱片，代表出貨量達到150萬張，並成為瑪丹娜於當地最暢銷的專輯<ref name="german ifpi"/>。由於在歐洲多國獲得商業成功，專輯亦登上{{tsl|en|European Top 100 Albums|歐洲專輯百強榜|歐洲專輯百強榜}}冠軍位置<ref name="hitsoftheworld"/>，並獲[[國際唱片業協會|國際唱片業協會]]認證為七白金唱片，代表於歐洲的出貨量達到700萬張，成為1998年至2007年期間{{tsl|en|List of best-selling albums in Europe|歐洲最暢銷專輯列表|歐洲第三暢銷專輯}}<ref name="euro ifpi"/><ref>{{cite web|title=IFPI Platinum Europe Awards: Best-selling albums in Europe over the past decade (1998-2007)|publisher=IFPI|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/platinum-europe-awards-2007.pdf|accessdate=2014-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130725051454/http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/platinum-europe-awards-2007.pdf|archive-date=2013-07-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《光芒萬丈》亦於世界其他地方獲得商業成功，包括登上比利時、荷蘭、芬蘭、希臘、匈牙利、以色列、挪威、新加坡、西班牙與瑞士的專輯榜冠軍<ref name="spain"/><ref name="hungmedien"/>。專輯其後成為[[華納音樂集團|華納音樂集團]]於1998年在[[亚太地区|亚太地区]]最暢銷的專輯<ref name="asia">{{cite journal|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JQoEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA62-IA4&dq=Warner+Music%27s+most+successful+international+albums+in+the+region+this+year+include+Madonna%27s+Ray+of+Light+(400,000)&hl=es-419&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjHtZn29N7TAhXH4yYKHVKCBC4Q6AEIKDAA#v=onepage&q=Warner%20Music%27s%20most%20successful%20international%20albums%20in%20the%20region%20this%20year%20include%20Madonna%27s%20Ray%20of%20Light%20(400%2C000)&f=false|title=Price Cutting, In-Store Performing, Megastore Opening|date=1998-10-24|accessdate=2017-05-07|work=Billboard|issn=0006-2510|volume=110|issue=43|page=62|journal=|archive-date=2020-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701152818/https://books.google.com/books?id=JQoEAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA62-IA4&dq=Warner+Music's+most+successful+international+albums+in+the+region+this+year+include+Madonna's+Ray+of+Light+(400,000)&hl=es-419&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjHtZn29N7TAhXH4yYKHVKCBC4Q6AEIKDAA#v=onepage&q=Warner%20Music%27s%20most%20successful%20international%20albums%20in%20the%20region%20this%20year%20include%20Madonna%27s%20Ray%20of%20Light%20(400%2C000)&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《光芒萬丈》於全球總共售出超過1,600萬張<ref>{{harvnb|Taraborrelli|2002|pp=303}}</ref><ref name="RayofLightsales">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2009/jul/05/william-orbit-tennyson-poem-verb|title=Orbit switches from Madonna to Tennyson with live Radio 3 epic|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|first=Vanessa|last=Thorpe|date=2009-07-05|accessdate=2012-01-04|archive-date=2013-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002143713/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2009/jul/05/william-orbit-tennyson-poem-verb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

